; Coverage test for xact.cc lines 612-613
; Tests balanced virtual null posting when virtual_balance is a long integer.
; When balanced virtual postings use commodityless amounts, the virtual_balance
; may be stored as a long, requiring conversion via to_amount().

2024/01/01 Test virtual long balance
    Expenses:A                 $50.00
    Assets:B
    [Budget:A]                      5
    [Budget:B]

test bal
             $-50.00  Assets:B
                   0  Budget
                   5    A
                  -5    B
              $50.00  Expenses:A
--------------------
                   0
end test
